.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-LOCAL-PCT-STDDEV" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-local-pct-stddev \- FEAT-2708 peer-local-pct-stddev
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-local-pct-stddev
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the standard deviation of local balance percentage per peer (FEAT-2708).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN containing \fBlocal_pct_stddev_peer\fR (float) and \fBsample_size\fR (int).
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
